name: PoochFacts
0:
”Alexa, open Pooch Facts”
”Alexa, start Pooch Facts”
”Alexa, ask Pooch Facts for a fact”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: pooch facts
des:
I just want to share the love of information for our pooches. Please leave a comment to help me make this better and more unique for an enhanced experience for yourself and others. Pooch facts are here with a few quips sprinkled in. Do you want straight facts or more quips? Leave a comment and I will address them accordingly. 
When using the skill, you can say "Alexa, next" to move to the next fact. 
At any point, you can say "Alexa, stop" to exit the skill.
Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
